                    <p class="font-bold">Let's do the maths:</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 font-mono text-sm md:text-base">
                        <li class="flex justify-between">
                            <span>Average tradie job:</span>
                            <span class="font-bold">$2,500</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between items-center text-signal font-bold">
                            <span>One extra job/week:</span>
                            <span>$130,000/yr</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex justify-between text-gray-500">
                            <span>YourHQ:</span>
